<p>I'm not sure if this will work or not, but here's my idea. <br /> <br />I've been 52thf for the last week now and I'm having a horrible time finding parties.&nbsp;&nbsp;There's usually not enough of the right jobs seeking to start one and I've gone over 10hrs at a time seeking. (doing quests and other things during this time, but the flag and search comments were up) So I get bored and tried to level a lower job, but how am I to be found if someone lvl 52 needs a thf?  <br /> <br />So what I'm proposing is a thread where anyone lvl 50-75 who wouldn't mind getting an invite while leveling another job posts thier info here.  If I get enough positive feedback I'd like to make this a sticky that I'd update daily.  I'll post an example of the kind of format I'm thinking of: <br /> <br />Alexandra:  52thf @3k <br />SJ: nin, war <br /> <br />The format wouldn't have to be like that, but limit it to 2-3 lines per character. <br /> <br />Someone can then send me a /tell if they needed a thf while I was leveling blm in kazham, and I would politely tell my party I was leaving and find a replacement if possible. <br /> <br />Any thoughts or ideas?</p>
