<p> I know how ya feel, just gotta remember that some jobs are vital to parties (WHM RDM PLD/WAR/NIN), while others must compete with like jobs (all other jobs (the DDs) other than BST). <br /> <br /> As your a damage-dealing profession (and especially as a THF), you must do everything in your power to blow the socks off of every party member in every party you get. This is especally true with THF as it is easy to screw up the THF job, THF requires more skill and manipulation than any other job in the game.&nbsp;&nbsp;It's a challenge, but the key thing to anyDD job is reputation.  Build this and your path to higherlevels will open. <br /> <br /> That, or: <br /> <br /><blockquote><b class="sm">Quote:</b><hr size="1" />level beastmaster? <hr size="1" /></blockquote></p>
